50|$|Scott Clinic, a <b>medium</b> <b>secure</b> <b>unit</b> {{initially}} housed on Rainford Ward on the Sherdley Division (but later {{moving to}} its own purpose built accommodation after the original hospital buildings were demolished), is the only mental health facility that {{is located on the}} former Sherdley Division site and the Rainhill Hospital site as a whole.|$|E
